{"tid":2169370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［正視聽］有無諗過英文揸兜都可以做對外文宣?","createTime":"2020-08-22T12:28:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T12:38:21.000Z","uid":259507,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a3e4b2837ff9ea2d37c5ccd10037e383525ad365","tid":2169370,"uid":259507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T12:28:50.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">就係做Reddit task啦</span></span><br />\nReddit基本上係外國版連登<br />\n國際網上論壇，有4億外國人用！<br />\n好L大條戰線！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">(雖然reddit係紅底同收左騰訊錢，但冇證據顯示騰訊目前左右到Reddit運作，大股東仍然係美國Advance Publications)</span><br />\n<br />\n一隻雞腸唔識都ok, 慢慢學都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">(唔想睇字嘅，教學圖喺下面)</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">1. Download Reddit app</span><br />\nApple: <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/reddit/id1064216828\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Freddit%2Fid1064216828&d=aFiO92UEzPWfS5u3FViI6YPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=6eaec263\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/us/app/reddit/id1064216828</a><br />\nAndroid: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.reddit.frontpage\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.reddit.frontpage&d=aFiO92UEzPWfS5u3FViI6YPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=692809d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.reddit.frontpage</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">2. 打開個app -&gt; Get Started -&gt; 註冊acc</span><br />\n(最好用鬼email)<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">3. 上 <a href=\"https://www.Act4HK.com/Reddit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Act4HK.com%2FReddit&d=aFiO92UEzPWfS5u3FViI6YPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=dc736d75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.Act4HK.com/Reddit</a></span><br />\n撳入個post<br />\n入app版面<br />\n撳upvote<br />\n(upvote係向上箭咀，撳完會變橙紅色)<br />\n(唔好comment，講錯嘢就唔好)<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">4. 撳返入Act4HK<br />\n撳入下一個post</span><br />\n(已完成嘅: 灰色圓圈會變成綠色)<br />\n<br />\n全程唔使用英文！！<br />\n睇唔明都唔緊要，Act4HK揀得嘅全部都要推！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n抗爭唔係一日嘅事<br />\n堅持先會贏<br />\n每日都要做task<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n <span class=\"small\">順便簡介下：<br />\nMod/moderator = 版務管理員，本身都係用戶<br />\n<br />\nSub/subreddit = 版，用r/代表，例如: r/HongKong，其實好似連登嘅「台」，不過多好多，而且每一個sub都有自己嘅規則、mods<br />\n<br />\nUser/redditor = 用戶，用u/代表，例如: u/spez<br />\n<br />\nUpvote / Downvote = 上下箭嘴 = 正/負皮，用以提高/降低Post嘅能見度<br />\n<br />\nUpvote同downvote中間個數就係&ldquo;正皮減負皮&rdquo;</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\">【Reddit文宣部】<br />\nTg頻道： <a href=\"http://t.me/reddithk_channel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Freddithk_channel&d=aFiO92UEzPWfS5u3FViI6YPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=9cbb8b50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/reddithk_channel</a><br />\nTwitter：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Reddit_freeHK?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FReddit_freeHK%3Fs%3D09&d=aFiO92UEzPWfS5u3FViI6YPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=afef4754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Reddit_freeHK?s=09</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yef7kzT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYef7kzT.jpg&h=94e735cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aim6A8f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Faim6A8f.jpg&h=493d41e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UWRZbGz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUWRZbGz.jpg&h=9acf56e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ab5db9d73e87232aa42efcd42992de9c0d5a3ed","tid":2169370,"uid":48083,"lik